<lb n="0883b02"/><head type="no">No. 1364 [No. 1363]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0883b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0883003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>妙臂印幢陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0883b04"/>
<lb n="0883b05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0883004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【三】</note><note n="0883004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔大〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883004"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>唐<note n="0883005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（天后代）＋于【宋】【元】</note><app n="0883005"><lem>于</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">天后代于</rdg></app>闐三藏實叉難陀<note n="0883006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔奉制〕－【三】</note><note n="0883006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔奉制〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883006"><lem>奉　制</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0883b06"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在雞羅娑山諸獸依處妙
<lb n="0883b07"/>宮殿中。與大比丘眾千二百五十人。又與無
<lb n="0883b08"/>量菩薩摩訶薩俱。文殊師利法王子而為上
<lb n="0883b09"/>首。靡不皆如童子之形。并賢護等十六丈夫</p>
<lb n="0883b10"/><p>爾時世尊以正念<note n="0883007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】</note><note n="0883007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智＝知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883007"><lem>智</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>。為諸天人演說法要皆
<lb n="0883b11"/>令歡喜。時大梵王及諸天龍夜叉乾闥婆阿
<lb n="0883b12"/>修羅迦樓羅緊那羅摩&CB00264;羅伽人非人等。各
<lb n="0883b13"/>起合掌前白佛言。世尊有諸眾生。由造種種
<lb n="0883b14"/>罪惡業故。應墮地獄餓鬼畜生。閻魔羅界備
<lb n="0883b15"/>受眾苦。唯願世尊大悲。為說除滅如是苦惱
<lb n="0883b16"/>方便。令彼眾生皆得解脫諸惡道難。時觀自
<lb n="0883b17"/>在菩薩摩訶薩。復與無量持&CB00057;大仙前後圍
<lb n="0883b18"/>繞。頂禮佛足白言世尊。<note n="0883008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】</note><note n="0883008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883008"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>垂愍念以善方
<lb n="0883b19"/>便救諸世間。佛言善男子。有陀羅尼名妙臂
<lb n="0883b20"/>印幢。若能常念誦習思惟。速得除滅五無間
<lb n="0883b21"/>罪。富貴安樂大姓家生。爾時世尊即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0883b22"/><p type="dharani">怛姪他迦<note place="inline">居伽反下同</note>囉迦囉<note place="inline">一</note>枳利枳<note n="0883009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＋（二）夾註【三】</note><note n="0883009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＋（二）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883009"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">利<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>句嚕句
<lb n="0883b23"/>嚕<note place="inline">三</note>娑囉娑囉<note place="inline">四</note>徙唎徙唎<note place="inline">五</note>蘇嚕蘇嚕　薩婆
<lb n="0883b24"/>佛陀阿婆盧枳帝<note place="inline">七</note><note n="0883010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陀＝柁【三】＊</note><note n="0883010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀＝柁【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0883010"><lem>陀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">柁</rdg></app>囉<app type="＊" source="0883010"><lem>陀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">柁</rdg></app>囉<note place="inline">八</note>達摩阿婆
<lb n="0883b25"/>盧枳帝<note place="inline">九</note>蔗囉蔗囉<note place="inline">十</note>僧伽阿提瑟恥帝<note place="inline">十一</note>跋
<lb n="0883b26"/>囉跋囉<note place="inline">下囉字長聲</note>阿佞迦<note place="inline">十二</note>佛陀俱胝婆瑟低<note place="inline">十
<lb n="0883b27"/>三</note>&CB00890;<note place="inline"><note n="0883011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">初＝祛【三】</note><note n="0883011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">初＝祛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883011"><lem>初</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">祛</rdg></app>覲反</note>那&CB00890;那<note place="inline">十四</note>薩婆阿跋囉那<note place="inline">去聲</note>&CB00135;寐
<lb n="0883b28"/><note place="inline">十五</note>薩婆毒佉阿婆那<note place="inline">去聲</note>耶<note place="inline">十六</note>勃&CB00691;多勃&CB00691;
<lb n="0883b29"/>多<note place="inline">十七</note>姪曬多姪曬多<note place="inline">十八</note>怛吒<note place="inline"><note n="0883012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00250;＝襟【三】</note><note n="0883012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00250;＝襟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0883012"><lem>&CB00250;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">襟</rdg></app>迦反</note>怛吒<note place="inline">十九</note>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1364.0883c" n="0883c"/>
<lb n="0883c01"/>薩普吒耶<note place="inline">餘河反</note>薩普吒耶<note place="inline">二十</note>薩婆阿跋囉那阿
<lb n="0883c02"/>播耶<note place="inline">二十一</note>突揭帝寧<note place="inline">二十二</note>蘇婆呵<note place="inline">二十三</note></p>
<lb n="0883c03"/><p>善男子此陀羅尼。&M010527;河沙等諸佛所說。阿難
<lb n="0883c04"/>佛世難遇人身難得。受持此&CB00057;轉復為難。善
<lb n="0883c05"/>男子我念往昔。毘婆尸佛次第乃至迦葉如
<lb n="0883c06"/>來。咸為我說此陀羅尼。普欲安樂諸眾生故。
<lb n="0883c07"/>於諸佛所皆親聽受。爾時世尊說此&CB00057;已。觀
<lb n="0883c08"/>自在菩薩摩訶薩等。及天龍八部一切眾會。
<lb n="0883c09"/>聞佛所說皆大歡喜信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0883c10"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>妙臂印幢陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
